{{unreferenced|date=June 2008}}
The following closely related categories of '''[[forced labor]] in the [[Soviet Union]]''' may be distinguished.

*Pre-Gulag forced labor of the early [[Soviet  Russia]] and [[Soviet Union]] 
*The [[Gulag]] system, 
*[[Foreign forced labor in the Soviet Union]] of 1939-1954 which included labor of the [[World War II]] [[prisoners of war]] and [[internee]]s.
*Post-[[Stalin]] [[penal labor]] in the Soviet Union: [[Corrective labor colony]] (<U+0418><U+0441><U+043F><U+0440><U+0430><U+0432><U+0438><U+0442><U+0435><U+043B><U+044C><U+043D><U+043E>-<U+0442><U+0440><U+0443><U+0434><U+043E><U+0432><U+0430><U+044F> <U+043A><U+043E><U+043B><U+043E><U+043D><U+0438><U+044F>, <U+0418><U+0422><U+041A>) , [[Colony-settlement]] (<U+041A><U+043E><U+043B><U+043E><U+043D><U+0438><U+044F>-<U+043F><U+043E><U+0441><U+0435><U+043B><U+0435><U+043D><U+0438><U+0435>), [[corrective labor without incarceration]] (<U+0418><U+0441><U+043F><U+0440><U+0430><U+0432><U+0438><U+0442><U+0435><U+043B><U+044C><U+043D><U+044B><U+0435> <U+0440><U+0430><U+0431><U+043E><U+0442><U+044B> <U+0431><U+0435><U+0437> <U+043B><U+0438><U+0448><U+0435><U+043D><U+0438><U+044F> <U+0441><U+0432><U+043E><U+0431><U+043E><U+0434><U+044B>).

